{"tid":1460220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請珍惜最後8月兩星期！","createTime":"2019-08-13T01:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T03:14:53.000Z","uid":259821,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1f0351d75bbda08ff0641d93a040b322652cc775","tid":1460220,"uid":259821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:54:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲有兩星期學生們就會番學，平日要咁多人出到黎再唔係易事，而且打鐵趁熱，呢排一連串發生咁多事，琴日大家演習左一次，係唔係應該要係呢幾日繼續出呢？</span>唔好俾件事淡。琴日雖然大家好多都比唔少資訊嚇走左，但事後大家都已經知好多資訊都係流，香港機場既重要性大家都估左，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家可以珍惜機場呢個地方唔好嚇怕，珍惜剩餘兩個星期全港最齊人既日子！</span></span>"},{"pid":"378c66f36dc6ed362ed0d4a95cc6023c75ac8315","tid":1460220,"uid":89184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:57:51.000Z","msg":"其實藍絲好純真，要佢地支持可能比想像中易<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438639\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438639</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"95068f1f0b89bd22e4b381d06ef5993f28eab40b","tid":1460220,"uid":142007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4904323e5706e7269a6b6e4362c765b3b09927","tid":1460220,"uid":25758,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:05:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我代港人宣怖，8月並唔撚係最後</span></span>"},{"pid":"311ea53c774415e3cde300ebd800cfddd002d9c0","tid":1460220,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:08:12.000Z","msg":"呢個係一個偽命題"},{"pid":"9d47d09142b2395b7cc353daf205a55bac68abc8","tid":1460220,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:09:10.000Z","msg":"On9,星期六日一樣可以繼續搞,而家多數D活動都係星期六日搞"},{"pid":"e27b574727a0dcb224fe977f4f642960ee60aba0","tid":1460220,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:09:15.000Z","msg":"已